This project builds on the Open Knowledge Format (OKF), an open specification
published by Google Cloud:
  https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/knowledge-catalog/tree/main/okf

OKF Hub is an independent open-source project. It is not affiliated with, nor
endorsed by, Google. "Open Knowledge Format" refers to the open specification as
published by Google Cloud.
